# Hotels template placeholders:
# {affiliateId} {destination} {checkIn} {checkOut} {adults}
# Cars template placeholders:
# {affiliateId} {pickupLocation} {dropoffLocation} {pickupDate} {dropoffDate} {pickupTime} {dropoffTime}
